'''Uwa''' was a type of wood native to [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaan]]. The Alderaanian embassy on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], [[Cantham House/Legends|Cantham House]], had a hallway with panels of uwa wood leading to the [[White Room]].

After Alderaan's destruction [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo's]] old friend [[Roa]] was lucky enough to find some uwa wood on a salvaged [[Alderaanian pleasure craft]], which he used on his [[SoroSuub Corporation/Legends|SoroSuub]] [[Personal Luxury Yacht 3000/Legends|Personal Luxury Yacht 3000]], ''[[Happy Dagger]]''.

